          "email": "nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com",
          "date": "2013-08-20 20:30:30.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-3522 osd-zfs: Report ZFS blocksize as 4K",
        "message": "LU-3522 osd-zfs: Report ZFS blocksize as 4K\n\nThis will cause ofd to do rational grants instead of trying to\ngrant wildly too much space for each write.  Without this change\nofd assumed that all grants would take up 32x the amount of space\nbecuase zfs reported a block size of 128KB.\n\nTest-Parameters: mdsfilesystemtype=zfs mdtfilesystemtype=zfs  ostfilesystemtype=zfs testlist=sanity-benchmark,sanity,conf-sanity\nSigned-off-by: Nathaniel Clark <nathaniel.l.clark@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Ie67a7e9379b37f3c307cc1da9a9127865e172ff5\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
